data.description: Beautiful, less than 1 year old home w/ covered front porch & back patio w/ ceiling fan/lighting. Great room offers living, kitchen, & dining space. Kitchen features SS appliances, quartz countertops & breakfast bar/ island with outlets. Luxurious, built-in, electric fireplace is centerpiece of living area. Large master bedroom w/ master bath that boasts double vanity sink, tiled walk in shower, and oversized walk in closet. Access to laundry room from master bedroom & sitting room off of garage. Both 2nd & 3rd bedrooms are nicely sized, each with their own walk-in closet. 2nd bath also has double vanity sink w/ tub/shower combo. Clean look w/ recessed lighting. Oversized att 2 car garage allows for additional storage.
